  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <lg xml:id="TolC075">
        <l>nāṉkā kuvatē</l>
	<l>ku eṉap peyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi</l>
	<l>yepporu ḷāyiṉuṅ koḷḷu matuvē.</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/57/mode/1up">57</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/58/mode/1up">58</ref>.</p>
      <p><note xml:lang="en">Verses 74 and 75 are considered one verse here.</note></p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tāmōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n81/mode/1up">78</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n81/mode/1up">78</ref>.</p>
<p>i - ḷ. mēl ku eṉap peyar koṭuttōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaiccol nāṉkāvatām. atu yātāṉumoruporuḷāyiṉum ataṉaiyēṟṟuniṟkum. e-ṟu.</p>
<p>u - m.</p> 
  <lg xml:id="TolC075-Cēṉ-cit1">
    <l>antaṇaṟkāvaik koṭuttāṉ</l>
  </lg> 
  <p>eṉa varum.</p>
  <lg xml:id="TolC075-Cēṉ-cit2">
    <l>māṇākkaṟku nūṟporuḷuraittāṉ</l>
  </lg>
   <p>eṉak koṭaip poruḷavākiya collāṉaṉṟip piṟavāypaṭṭāṟkūṟappaṭuvaṉavum,</p> 
   <lg xml:id="TolC075-Cēṉ-cit3">
    <l>māṇākkaṟku aṟivu koṭuttāṉ</l>
  </lg> 
   <p>eṉak koṭuppāṉporuḷāyk koḷvāṉkaṭcellātu āṇṭut tōṉṟum poruḷumellāmaṭaṅkutaṟku epporuḷāyiṉumeṉṟār.</p>
  <p>piṟaporuḷumuḷavāyiṉum, kōṭaṟporuḷ ciṟantamaiyiṉ, epporuḷāyiṉuṅkoḷḷumeṉṟār.	(14)</p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/n121/mode/1up">93</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, muṟaiyāṉē nāṉkāva tipporuṭkaṇ varu meṉkiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) ku eṉappeyariya vēṟṟumaik kiḷavi nāṉkākuvatē ― mēṟ ku veṉap peyar koṭut tōtappaṭṭa vēṟṟumaic coṉ ṉāṉkāvatām, atu epporuḷāyiṉuṅ koḷḷum ― aḵtu yātāṉumoru poruḷāyiṉu mataṉait tāṉēṟṟu niṟkumeṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC075-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>antaṇar kāvaik koṭuttāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC075-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>māṇākkaṟku nūṟporu ḷuraittāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉak koṭaipporuḷavākiya collāṉaṉṟip piṟavāy pāṭṭāṟ kūṟuvaṉavum,
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC075-Nacc-cit3">
       <l>māṇākkaṟ kaṟivu koṭuttāṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
        eṉak koṭuppāṉ poruḷāyk koḷvāṉ kaṭ cellā tāṇṭut tōṉṟum poruḷu maṭakkutaṟ kepporu ḷāyiṉu meṉṟār.  <num xml:lang="en">(14)</num>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n68/mode/1up">61</ref>.</p>
      <p>
nāṉkām vēṟṟumaiyāmāṟu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
i-ḷ. nāṉkām vēṟṟumaiyāvatu ku eṉap peyarpeṟṟa vēṟṟumaiccol. aḵtu yātāṉumoru poruḷāyiṉum ēṟṟu niṟkum nilaimaittu. e-ṟu. eṉavē, ēṟkum poruṇmaikkaṇvarum. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC075-Teyv-cit1">
       <l>antaṇarkkuk koṭuttāṉ</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
eṉavarum.	[13]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Kallāṭaṉār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Cuntaramūrtti</persName> 1964, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/TVG27Tolkappiyam/page/70/mode/1up">70</ref>.</p>
      <p>
        <note xml:lang="ta">itaṉaiyum aṭutta nūṟpāvaiyum iṇaittu orē nūṟpāvākak koḷvar iḷampūraṇar.</note>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
